{"tid":1757391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（狂賀）正式宣布香港人已贏，立法會繼續努力就得～！","createTime":"2019-11-26T13:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T11:44:35.000Z","uid":19445,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7351b7f0407c38e8f72f051ca9ca2c1fc994bd59","tid":1757391,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:20:58.000Z","msg":"屌你地咪撚再推咩立法會，推返行動po得唔得<br />\n出年先選呀大佬，定當抗爭完左？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次區選除左當係民意授權之外根本冇撚用<br />\n事實證明好多人撐我地，但唔代表我地有實際成果 <br />\n你想要既結果係泛民贏，定係想要民主同普選。<br />\n<br />\n仲推個啲咩立法會點先唔輸個啲 我屌你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7.1 衝立法會個一刻 唔係已經豁左出去 宣布議會既不合法性喇咩？當日就已經證明香港人既決心<br />\n我可以同你講 有功能組別 點選都輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現實啲諗，出年係可能都冇普選，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但依家係咪冇更緊急既事可以做？定已經當抗爭完左？</span><br />\n<br />\n你要建制派輸，<br />\n只有一個方法：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">繼續抗爭，直到有普選為止</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知每個人做到既野好少，但心態上要改變<br />\n停止打飛機，推行動Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個人都做到！<br />\n<br />\n制度內抗爭，香港人試左廿年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好話咩雙軌並行一齊做（就算我比你拎六成直選，功能組別一樣輸到仆直）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係個句<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你想建制立法會輸 得一個方法<br />\n繼續抗爭 直到有普選</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔理遊行又好罷工又好裝修又有，真係唔想比人講中，選舉完抒發晒民怨就完，我地由此至始都冇獲得過啲咩，但損失左既係手足既命，佢地既前途。"},{"pid":"c663cdff1425ddca5be1ba861390d978d4b5bcde","tid":1757391,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:22:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7f5331ed12baae1686443fc1302093b439bd829","tid":1757391,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a9f8d9e13d6ed9e05bfe5d81f7a2bcf509af0a","tid":1757391,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0c8b076eefceb6921f7b65e37b218e8690098d","tid":1757391,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:39:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe69210eb772202a58fd5c8906768c3b8c6fc4c2","tid":1757391,"uid":62523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:40:56.000Z","msg":"抗爭暫時告一段落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474215d268449c86613629a353919ce7a75d5eeb","tid":1757391,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:47:27.000Z","msg":"好文一推"},{"pid":"cb8e775447a229a562b6a42a7ace376b9c08dcd8","tid":1757391,"uid":333741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:48:58.000Z","msg":"香港人需要休息 回氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936439ac523690fdc8d31fa2d80010f1cf00232b","tid":1757391,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:13:21.000Z","msg":"大家已經唔記得點解7.1要衝<br />\n要有險可守 一早唔洗抗爭啦<br />\n制度內抗爭試左咁多年 依家仲討論點玩？"},{"pid":"0a9e0c068228dcff810487aa0ebaea114b2413d2","tid":1757391,"uid":260830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:23:57.000Z","msg":"點解無人提起，就算比你有普選，你都係要打選戰<br />\n街頭抗爭係要有，但係選舉準備，爭民心，研究地區議題呢啲點都唔可以無掛？"},{"pid":"3fd25f2d538af2ee51d3f647627891959c09d963","tid":1757391,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a9e0c068228dcff810487aa0ebaea114b2413d2","tid":1757391,"uid":260830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:23:57.000Z","msg":"點解無人提起，就算比你有普選，你都係要打選戰<br />\n街頭抗爭係要有，但係選舉準備，爭民心，研究地區議題呢啲點都唔可以無掛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:26:58.000Z","msg":"佢哋依家係討論緊點樣係現行制度下取得大多數議席<br />\n包括點配票 同點係功能組別拎到議席<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有成年先選 但抗爭仲進行緊<br />\n咁點解唔努力啲諗有咩行動可以做"},{"pid":"354e941633469be3f56a3526018e0bdb6191d7d2","tid":1757391,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:27:17.000Z","msg":"呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，<br />\n以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQj1KLO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQj1KLO.jpg&h=ed72b375&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8510615e00497e572e742a1e2d56d4b74f2c8f2f","tid":1757391,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:29:49.000Z","msg":"唔可以放棄任何一個可以贏嘅方法"},{"pid":"96bd49a11a25dfb38b1cf14112b055ba9136f978","tid":1757391,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:32:24.000Z","msg":"一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭<br />\n<br />\n為咗班泛民左膠step brake幾多次?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等埋人權法先,等埋區選先,不如等埋維尼登基先?<br />\n<br />\n我就無咩氣打落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d584930c8ea8f0fcba3456f9d3855ce06bba726","tid":1757391,"uid":76347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:35:53.000Z","msg":"出面真係好多意見<br />\n呢個又話點、果個又話咁<br />\n我覺得最少都搞啲嘢先<br />\n唔好理激進定和平<br />\n最緊要係食到個勢 帶返個我地先係主場既訊息出嚟"},{"pid":"c5f62c870a7de2af0fe7322d4e9c7f9eaf5da26e","tid":1757391,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:40:38.000Z","msg":"係呀係呀, 出多幾個呢D POST場運場可以淡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37f230ed803e1561212f160897135ed5e02ccb8","tid":1757391,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:35:51.000Z","msg":"認同 推"},{"pid":"0110f20f261351ec615776771f001d4cef5b1a4b","tid":1757